A majestic ancient oak tree with an intricate root system visible beneath the soil surface, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style. The roots glow with warm amber light, forming an interconnected network underground that mirrors the sprawling branches above. The canopy is lush with vibrant emerald leaves, with small glowing orbs floating between branches suggesting connection and energy flow. Tiny forest spirits tend to different parts of the tree - some nurturing roots below ground, others caring for branches above. Soft golden afternoon light filters through the leaves, casting dappled shadows. The composition shows both the underground root network and the full crown in perfect balance, emphasizing the symbiotic relationship between hidden foundations and visible growth. Whimsical clouds drift in a pale blue sky. Rich, warm color palette with deep browns, luminous greens, and touches of magical gold.
